Having a Node with multiple components
Subscribing both to  E_NODEREMOVED   & E_COMPONENTREMOVED  (having 2 EventHandlers )

Once removing that Node  from the Scene ( Node::Remove() )
**Expected behaviour ( I might be wrong)**
I would expect  both EventHandlers to be called 
Once for the E_NODEREMOVED   EventHandler
Multiple times for E_COMPONENTREMOVED  EventHandler (depends on components amount)

**Actual behaviour** 
Only  the E_NODEREMOVED   EventHandler  is called .

**It  is caused due to the fact that** 

Scene::NodeRemoved(Node* node) 
{
...
   node->ResetScene();      // scene_ = 0  
}


void Node::RemoveComponent(Vector<SharedPtr<Component> >::Iterator i)
{
    if (Refs() > 0 && scene_)  // scene_ =0  event is not sent
    {
         ...
          scene_->SendEvent(E_COMPONENTREMOVED, eventData);
    }
}

