```
Vector.h:911:24: error: no matching function for call to ‘Urho3D::PODVector<int>::EraseSwap(Urho3D::PODVector<int>::Iterator&)’
```

RemoveSwap() is calling EraseSwap() and passing an iterator, but EraseSwap() expects a position.
```cpp
    bool RemoveSwap(const T& value)
    {
        Iterator i = Find(value);
        if (i != End())
        {
            EraseSwap(i);
            return true;
        }
        else
            return false;
    }
```
Signature of EraseSwap():
```cpp
void EraseSwap(unsigned pos, unsigned length = 1)
```

